{"tid":327974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴重疏忽！台灣向日本借展的文物從展架脫落受損","createTime":"2017-07-19T08:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T09:20:14.000Z","uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2b41083bcbd33dc164d3533772ff70f556d627","tid":327974,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"台灣故宮南院向日本借展的一件伊萬里青花瓷盤從展架脫落受損，日方人員將到當地檢查。<br />\n<br />\n被發現損毀的是這件全名為「青花柳葉鳥紋盤」，是西元1660年至1670年的日本江戶時代製造，至今已有三百多年歷史。<br />\n<br />\n故宮南院表示，工作人員是在周二早上開館前，進行例行檢查時發現文物從展架上移位脫落受損，已經緊急通報日方；又說今次展覽布置的相關工作，都是日方負責指揮，而在布置完成後，博物院並沒有移動任何展品。<br />\n<br />\n日方已經要求當局不要移動文物，並封鎖展櫃，下午將派人前往詳細檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f031a392ba9cb723ff8bfb260be9316e7724f6","tid":327974,"uid":114064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"比大陸好了，至少會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f32abeb707567ff4984b66ac482dd54128ea282","tid":327974,"uid":67302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"台日友好危在旦夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb29e9988f7a3d2bd5fe70abe88fcdc3cfb33357","tid":327974,"uid":17335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"有錄影架嘛<br />\n邊個出錯，一目了然啦"},{"pid":"92dc7f1a025dda2a50339d75543a958befb8f8e6","tid":327974,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾繁支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad37a96d846264cc3684457cbbcc4b6199ab83a","tid":327974,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco